channel.title: [PI] Auto Cache Downloader not unzipping cache
channel.description: So me and a friend of mine decided to make an RSPS, long story short, we encountered an issue, after finishing the RSPS, we got the website up and going, and now we wanted to make a webclient, so we needed an auto-cache downloader... Problem is... it doesn't unzip the cache it downloads, were using Deathlypvpz as a base, and it doesn't unzip the cache, plz help, we would like our webclient to work! :) Thanks!
